This is the plan for a new version of photoselect

Goals

1. Multithreaded decoding, image processing.
2. Cropping included.
3. Multiple views.
4. Comparison views.
5. Labeling
6. Grouping by date, time, camera, gps
7. Understands continuous shutter
8. Captions
9. Quick selection via thumbnails
10. Understands multiple screen displays

Non-goals

1. Editing beyond cropping
2. Storage
3. Upload
4. Webpage generation


